&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Company Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are the better way to work in finance. As private equity’s value creation partner, we sit at the heart of PE where sponsors and CFOs meet. Through financial consulting rooted in data, technology, and AI, we help clients drive value where we support the office of the CFO to drive end-to-end value creation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you crave challenging work and are looking to grow, come solve complex issues alongside 1,600+ finance &amp;amp; technology experts in a supportive, collaborative environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Backed by premier private equity firms and headquartered in New York with 11 offices around the globe, we are a high-growth, entrepreneurial firm looking for people who want to be part of building something great. Come make your mark.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data &amp;amp; Analytics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Accordion&#39;s Data &amp;amp; Analytics (D&amp;amp;A) team offers cutting-edge, intelligent solutions to a global clientele, leveraging a blend of domain knowledge, sophisticated technology tools, and deep analytics capabilities to tackle complex business challenges.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We partner with Private Equity clients and their Portfolio Companies across diverse sectors, including Retail, CPG, Healthcare, Media &amp;amp; Entertainment, Technology, and Logistics.&lt;/p&gt;
