&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Incident Investigation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Investigate output-quality incidents, orchestration failures, prompt/workflow regressions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Distinguish true software defects from model behavior, data-quality, or process issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Engineering, QA, and business stakeholders on judgment-heavy incidents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Controls&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support human-review patterns, fallback routes, and safe-operating responses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and apply production review practices for higher-risk workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document evidence and issue patterns for repeatability and release decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cover vendor-deployed solutions with same rigor as internally built workflows: managing vendor SLAs, update cycles, and incident patterns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Measurement Contribution&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
