&lt;h3&gt;AI System Readiness Vice President&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Vice President of AI System Readiness plays a pivotal role in preparing Accordion’s enterprise environments, data, and processes for AI enablement. Reporting directly to the AI Enablement Lead, this role bridges the gap between technology infrastructure, data architecture, and AI activation—ensuring the foundation is set for intelligent automation, advanced analytics, and generative AI capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
